274
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] I pomislio sam, znaš, to nije dobro mjesto za biti.

275
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] Trebam samo spremiti stvari.

276
00:28:35,279 --> 00:28:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] I to je nekako odakle je došla ideja.

277
00:28:39,599 --> 00:28:41,440
